caller_intent: The caller attempted to reach Heather Jones regarding an unresolved issue, expressing concern that Heather had not responded to previous messages despite being at work.
resolution_steps: Agent informed caller Heather Jones was out of the office until 2:00 PM.
Agent asked if caller wanted to leave a voicemail for Heather.
Caller declined and requested to speak with another agent.
Agent transferred the call to another agent.
knowledge_required: Heather Jones' work schedule and availability
Standard procedures for handling calls when an agent is unavailable
summary: A caller attempted to reach Heather Jones but was informed she was out of the office. The caller expressed concern about not receiving a response to previous messages. The agent transferred the call to another agent to address the issue.
